OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith showery rain spreading northeast.
OL,7,FRemaining mostly cloudy this afternoon
OL,8,Fwith patchy rain in the west, but dry
OL,9,Fin the east. Chance of some brightness
OL,10,Fin the Central Belt where it will be
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,14,Fclear periods. Then the rest of the
OL,15,Fnight will remain dry across all parts
OL,16,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,19,Fspreading eastwards across all parts,
OL,20,Fbut dry in the east in the morning.
OL,21,FMild in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
