OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAfter a
OL,6,Fchilly start on Friday it will be a
OL,7,Fdry and sunny day. Dry and bright on
OL,8,FSaturday but clouding over later.
OL,9,FCloudy with occasional rain on Sunday.
